<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.3.3">
<l>veyya ṉāyula kēḻuṭaṉ nalintava ṉuṭalaka mirupiḷavā</l>
<l>kaiyil nīḷukirp paṭaiyatu vāyttava ṉēyeṉak karuḷpuriyē</l>
<l>maiyi ṉārtaru varāliṉam pāyavaṇ taṭattiṭaik kamalaṅkaḷ</l>
<l>teyva nāṟumoṇ poykaikaḷ cūḻtiru veḷḷaṟai niṉṟāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[Lord] who pierced with the long claw weapons on [his] hands,</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the body and chest</l>
<l>Of the cruel one, the one who tormented the seven worlds all at once,</l>
<l rend="indent">became two pieces, grant me grace,</l>
<l>[Lord] who stands in Tiruveḷḷaṟai, encircled by bright springs,</l>
<l rend="indent">where lovely lotuses in the center of the fertile ponds</l>
<l>Waft fragrance, while schools of black murrel [fish],</l>
<l rend="indent">which naturally resemble black ink, leap.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
